Dorsal (above, left) and ventral (above, right) view of the skull and lower jaw (below) of MUSM 14154, a female specimen of 
<taxonomicName box="[369,512,1944,1967]" class="Mammalia" family="Didelphidae" genus="Marmosa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Didelphimorphia" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="andersoni">
